pageContext.claim: “But you know the nice part? There was no collusion. There was no obstruction. There was no anything. So that's the nice part. There was no phone calls, no nothing.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump does not know the conclusions of the investigation led by special prosecutor Robert Mueller. So far, the probe has turned up dozens of contacts between Trump campaign officials and Russia-linked people and entities -- contacts that Trump previously said did not exist.
